After being disappointed by black plays with the same tired and hashed-over plots and over the top buffoonery, I was very pleasantly surprised by this production. It had just the right touch of humor and drama, and had me laughing one minute and tearing up the next. The acting was superbly professional. If you want to see a refreshing and satisfying play, check this one out! You will not be disappointed.

This is a great movie. The acting was superb and the plot was awesome. These things happen to us in life. Just as we think we've got it all sometimes the bottom does drop out from under us. I enjoyed the way David E. Talbert handled the plot. There were some funny moments,, some sad moments, and some moments that made you go humm.... what would I do in that situation? I would definitely recommend it to a friend. Keep up the good work David E Talbert !!

What a great cast of characters. Funny and entertaining, that everyone can enjoy. I loved Garcelle Beauvais and Isaiah Washington together. I'm glad that I made this purchase. I usually enjoy David E. Talbert's plays. Suddenly Single is one I would watch again and a good addition to my collection.

Some overacting, but not a bad movie. I give it 4 stars because Garcelle did really good. There were some very honest parts and I'm glad I watched it. I love FANCY, and she did a great job. Its a good movie for single women to watch.

I LOVE LOVE LOVE David E. Talbert's plays and this one was really good. A lot of plays have meaningless scenes and dialogue and lose my attention, but I actually really liked the pacing and stayed engaged in the storyline throughout. Isaiah Washington is my baby daddy/husband in an alternate universe  (LOL!) and Garcelle displayed her beauty and talent (as always). I would definitely watch this again!
